This show is a true work of art... 

The story, the acting, the drama, the irony, the poetic moments, the subtleties, the way it is directed... Everything! It's very hard to find flaws in a show like this, when all these elements unite in a single, beautiful masterpiece.

If you haven't watched it yet, watch it! You will laugh, you will cry, you will enjoy a story full of surprising twists, meaningful subtleties, suspense, drama, tragedy, poetry, and a brilliant ending, with absolutely no loose ends.

This show must be watched and re-watched. It undoubtedly deserves the ranking 10.